Package problem2

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Author
    Class Author inherits Individual and stores first name and last name
    Band
    Class Band inherits Group and stores a name and a collection of RecordingArtists, the Band’s members
    Book
    Class Book inherits Item which has an Author as its creator.
    Catalog
    Class Catalog stores a collection of all the items in the library
    Creator
    Abstract class creator
    Group
    Abstract class Group inherits Creator
    Individual
    Abstract class Individual inherits Creator and stores first name and last name of an individual
    Item
    Abstract class Item stores information about item: the item’s creator, the item’s title and the year the item was released or published.
    Music
    Class Music inherits Item which can have either a RecordingArtist or a Band as its creator.
    RecordingArtist
    Class RecordingArtist inherits Individual and stores first name and last name
